{"tid":498280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃碧雲公開支持港獨","createTime":"2017-12-13T15:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T08:14:29.000Z","uid":389,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"41affcc2ccf28cf7eef320a1f1823212776db7fd","tid":498280,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"民主黨議員黃碧雲則指，下一場戰事將在明年3月立法會補選，香港人未來一定要團結，協助民主派在明年3.11補選「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全取四席，光復香港</span></span>」，希望巿民支持在民主派初選勝出的候選人，高喊：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「團結一致，團結議會，光復香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/233220_33c78b8176c5499a2b01ccf08635d92d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F233220_33c78b8176c5499a2b01ccf08635d92d.jpg&h=d78a8b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港為梁天琦競選口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/233607_d15821d6217567c155054486162bf5d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F233607_d15821d6217567c155054486162bf5d3.jpg&h=e3ecc7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/234017_f51a3e4b772917ef5c9b72d428be3c40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F234017_f51a3e4b772917ef5c9b72d428be3c40.jpg&h=6306874a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/233532_7346197f1d00d587c22d1ae4e15c13e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F233532_7346197f1d00d587c22d1ae4e15c13e7.jpg&h=48624fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎競選口號為「光復議會」，有先見之明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/234107_5d549c42a8748c06f476ad4d6035756b.jpg\" dat